# App endpoints (.http — use httpYac in Cursor; humao REST Client is broken there)
# Start server: make run  (or: uv run main)
# Environment: status bar → pick "local" (http-client.env.json)
# Send: click "Send" above a request (httpYac), or Cmd+Alt+R. Response reuses the right pane.

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000`

### Health — root
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### OpenAPI schema
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json

### Swagger UI
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs

### ReDoc
GET {{baseUrl}}/redoc
